    <briefdescription>
<para>Default deleter for <ref refid="classDali_1_1UniquePtr" kindref="compound">UniquePtr</ref>. </para>
    </briefdescription>
    <detaileddescription>
<para>Uses operator delete to free the managed object. Being an empty class, it qualifies for Empty Base Optimization (EBO) so that UniquePtr&lt;T&gt; (with the default deleter) does not waste memory storing the deleter.</para>
<para>@SINCE_2_5.19 <parameterlist kind="templateparam"><parameteritem>
<parameternamelist>
<parametername>Type</parametername>
</parameternamelist>
<parameterdescription>
<para>The type of the pointer to delete </para>
</parameterdescription>
</parameteritem>
</parameterlist>
</para>
